messages.text: Who cares if Ryan is 10 years older than you…
Oh sorry, I think you have the wrong number.
Oh, is that what he told you?
Ryan’s not who he says he is.
Lol and why should I listen to a complete stranger?
Because your life depends on it.
Wait – I’m not listening to another word unless you tell me who you are.
Did he tell you I was crazy?
He said that so you wouldn’t listen to me.
Why?! You’re just a psycho ex!
If you don’t listen to me, you’ll end up DEAD.
I’m not listening to your lies.
I know you have doubts about him.
Little things he does that make you worry.
Maybe you said the wrong thing once and he blew up at you?
Or maybe you forgot to text him and he flew into a rage?
And yes, he has a jealous streak—
And it’s going to get worse.
I barely escaped from Ryan with my life.
And I can’t stand by and do nothing as he does the same to you.
But everything changed during our honeymoon.
He took me to a remote camping site in the desert, near Joshua Tree.
The whole thing was planned out.
He nearly succeeded but I somehow fought my way out and escaped.
I was so shaken, so shocked…
We got married so quickly, I realized there was so much I didn’t know about him.
That’s when I started digging into his past.
I’m sorry, I just can’t believe that about Ryan.
Have you ever met his family?
No, but he was in and out of foster homes. He doesn’t really know his family.
Have you ever seen photos from his childhood?
I probably wouldn’t keep photos either?
Do you know any of Ryan’s close friends?
He works a lot, and when he’s not working he’s with me.
Doesn’t that seem strange to you?
That your only knowledge of Ryan is through what he’s told you?
No friends or family to back it up?
I know it’s hard to hear.
I don’t want to believe you…
But what am I supposed to do?
We were going to elope next weekend.
Ceremony in Vegas and then a week at a hotel in the Nevada desert.
My whole life is with Ryan now.
Do you have family you can stay with?
No, my family all lives out of state…
I’ve been out of work, I can’t afford it.
And Ryan manages all the money anyway.
I live in Addington, two hours away from you—
You could stay with me until you figure out something more permanent.
I’m not sure…wouldn’t that be weird?
Maybe, but do you have another option?
If you wait until Ryan gets home from work, he’ll know something’s up.
I can’t see him right now.
Drive to my place and you can call family from here.
Ok, but just for the night.
I’ll be on the road in ten minutes.
When you arrive, just come straight in.
I’ll be down in the basement working.
The body of Lucy Kahn was found this morning in Addington, VA, inside the home of Katie Garcia.
Paramedics were called to the scene, but pronounced Kahn dead upon arrival.
Garcia, who was vacant from the property and is suspected to be on the run, is wanted by police on prior counts of assault and kidnapping.
Garcia’s ex-husband and Kahn’s fiancé, Ryan Moore, spoke to the media stating that Garcia is mentally disturbed…
And has been harassing him since the dissolution of their own marriage
